{"tid":2327512,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"中科院發表調查報告　內地人月均休閒消費83人民幣","createTime":"2020-12-16T06:08:46.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-16T06:42:14.000Z","uid":54337,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"11fe708a0de666facaaa94cad550c506fb826c5c","tid":2327512,"uid":54337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-16T06:08:46.000Z","msg":"中科院發表調查報告 內地人月均休閒消費83人民幣<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/cnnews/20201216/mobile/bkn-20201216093809206-1216_00952_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fcnnews%2F20201216%2Fmobile%2Fbkn-20201216093809206-1216_00952_001.html&d=P3odlOe4J5oN5vIqyIzMU8FcVrLE0QCYyCuC44%2F36M0%3D&h=192f2970\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/cnnews/20201216/mobile/bkn-20201216093809206-1216_00952_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"7daa5c86a78b0f0a20ff551235e3251517f2d57f","tid":2327512,"uid":54337,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-16T06:09:01.000Z","msg":"中國社科院近日發布《休閒綠皮書：2019-2020年中國休閒發展報告》顯示，過去1年有44.4%內地人只花1,000元（人民幣，下同，約1,200港元）及以下在休閒消費開支上，換言之，即每人每月平均休閒支出僅83元（約100港元）。<br />\n<br />\n中國社科院旅遊研究中心的「中國國民休閒狀況調查（2020）」問卷調查結果顯示，過去1年，國民年均休閒消費為5,647元（約6,800港元）。其中，個人休閒消費在1,001至3,000元（約3,600港元）佔22.7%，3001至5000元（約5,600港元）佔10%，5,001至10,000元（約12,000港元）佔11.1%，休閒消費超過10,000元佔11.8%，44.4%受訪者休閒消費在1,000元及以下。<br />\n<br />\n台灣中經院副研究員吳明澤向外媒表示，調查結果顯示多數人較着重於基本生活消費，休閒消費較少，且內地低收入人口佔比仍然很高，貧富差距嚴重，不利於全面脫貧、進入全面小康，亦不利於未來靠擴大內需來支撐經濟。再者，中國計劃2035年要將人均GDP翻倍至2萬美元（約15.6萬港元），吳明澤認為難度相當高。"},{"pid":"f76e084f7d30e671e0b26b61550c23681de5a0c4","tid":2327512,"uid":54337,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-16T06:09:30.000Z","msg":"83蚊人仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4b6475699c32c0d50b09b1cfcc7d99b4317ac579","tid":2327512,"uid":152222,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-16T06:11:27.000Z","msg":"要不是大陸，香港..........<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"246e87e403edeea82615669bf088b36084dc3cc9","tid":2327512,"uid":75072,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-16T06:13:08.000Z","msg":"支那窮閪國"},{"pid":"04b3ff38c18be1add463be1938847667c910af84","tid":2327512,"uid":54337,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"4b6475699c32c0d50b09b1cfcc7d99b4317ac579","tid":2327512,"uid":152222,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-16T06:11:27.000Z","msg":"要不是大陸，香港..........<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-12-16T06:13:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://tvmost.com.hk/most/uploads/images/2015/Article/2015.05/2015.05.21/withoutchinese/01_640.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftvmost.com.hk%2Fmost%2Fuploads%2Fimages%2F2015%2FArticle%2F2015.05%2F2015.05.21%2Fwithoutchinese%2F01_640.jpg&h=452c83e4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n83蚊人仔就照顧到香港<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7d09e2bdec25ae0c689c786d97e319afa168f8ee","tid":2327512,"uid":152222,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"04b3ff38c18be1add463be1938847667c910af84","tid":2327512,"uid":54337,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"4b6475699c32c0d50b09b1cfcc7d99b4317ac579","tid":2327512,"uid":152222,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-16T06:11:27.000Z","msg":"要不是大陸，香港..........<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-12-16T06:13:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://tvmost.com.hk/most/uploads/images/2015/Article/2015.05/2015.05.21/withoutchinese/01_640.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftvmost.com.hk%2Fmost%